# =============================================================================
# POINTER ONLY — not a second env contract
# =============================================================================
#
# Canonical proxy environment template and live file:
#   infra/llm-gateway/.env.example
#   infra/llm-gateway/.env
#
# Setup:
#   cp infra/llm-gateway/.env.example infra/llm-gateway/.env
#   # edit infra/llm-gateway/.env — fill secrets
#   uv run llg up
#
# Root `docker-compose.yml` is an `include:` shim. From repo root, Compose still
# loads cwd `.env` for ${VAR} interpolation — so a root `.env` is a footgun.
# Prefer `uv run llg up`, or always:
#   docker compose --env-file infra/llm-gateway/.env -f docker-compose.yml …
# Do not create a root `.env` for the gateway stack.
#
# App clients use infra/llm-gateway/.env.app.example (virtual key + base URL).
# Never commit real `.env` files.
# =============================================================================
